{"tid":373731,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"大家玩過最好玩嘅海賊王遊戲係邊隻？","createTime":"2017-08-25T08:37:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-14T17:47:49.000Z","uid":23863,"like":6,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"538597f371dbb69a3de29fc52d37a6997872acaf","tid":373731,"uid":23863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T08:37:37.000Z","msg":"HI 又係我。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁近排ONE PIECE：UNLIMITED WORLD RED重製就出咗啦。<br />\n<br />\n我地個channel都諗住開個直播同大家一齊玩回味下嘅。<br />\n<br />\n咁但係我個腦就有個問題出咗嚟，就係咁多隻海賊王遊戲，有冇話邊隻係大家都鐘意嘅呢？<br />\n<br />\n所以就拍咗段片同大家分享下我嘅睇法嘅。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VaPv-GJyB2k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVaPv-GJyB2k&d=LVGNc7cxt5eQapPGOVlFvi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=e6d9266f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/VaPv-GJyB2k</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁大家睇完可以講下你地嘅意見啦，有機會可以一齊玩。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地個channel其實都仲有其他類型嘅片嘅，大家可以㩒入嚟望望㗎。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/happykongner\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fc%2Fhappykongner&d=LVGNc7cxt5eQapPGOVlFvi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=a475f627\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/c/happykongner</a><br />\n<br />\n我地都有Facebook Page㗎<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/happykongner/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhappykongner%2F&d=LVGNc7cxt5eQapPGOVlFvi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=41185c1a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/happykongner/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n多謝各位巴絲支持。<img 